00:13:06.316 --> 00:13:08.960 align:middle line:84%
when you get deep in your
soul-- wait a minute.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:11.680 align:middle line:84%
I have to pull myself
together, because this is big.

00:13:11.680 --> 00:13:13.870 align:middle line:90%
All right, hold it.

00:13:13.870 --> 00:13:19.600 align:middle line:84%
Sacred surrender is when you
get how powerful you are.

00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:24.610 align:middle line:84%
Not how unpowerful, but
how powerful you are.

00:13:24.610 --> 00:13:29.170 align:middle line:84%
What an incredibly powerful
instrument you really

00:13:29.170 --> 00:13:34.200 align:middle line:84%
are that every
thought you have is,

00:13:34.200 --> 00:13:38.850 align:middle line:84%
in fact, a tool of creation,
that every prayer you say

00:13:38.850 --> 00:13:40.560 align:middle line:90%
is, in fact, heard.

00:13:40.560 --> 00:13:43.380 align:middle line:84%
If you can get
over your own fear

00:13:43.380 --> 00:13:46.020 align:middle line:84%
