That didn't strike me as
good news when I realized it.

00:14:28.980 --> 00:14:32.820 align:middle line:84%
Because let's face it, this
is what spirituality is about.

00:14:32.820 --> 00:14:39.330 align:middle line:84%
You have to up the bar and
decide I have to work at this.

00:14:39.330 --> 00:14:41.490 align:middle line:84%
But then you have
to realize what does

00:14:41.490 --> 00:14:45.010 align:middle line:90%
