00:14:45.010 --> 00:14:47.790 align:middle line:84%
What does it mean
for the guidance

00:14:47.790 --> 00:14:51.270 align:middle line:84%
that I hear that I
have to surrender to?

00:14:51.270 --> 00:14:54.030 align:middle line:90%
What does it mean for that?

