so that you don't mess it up.

00:16:11.780 --> 00:16:15.360 align:middle line:84%
Now, the journey to
empowerment, oftentimes we

00:16:15.360 --> 00:16:20.330 align:middle line:84%
think of this spiritual journey
only in terms of ourself.

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:24.020 align:middle line:84%
My spiritual journey,
my spiritual journey.

00:16:24.020 --> 00:16:29.890 align:middle line:84%
But I have to tell you that this
spiritual journey is about how

00:16:29.890 --> 00:16:34.150 align:middle line:84%
