greater than ourselves

00:16:34.150 --> 00:16:39.960 align:middle line:84%
on behalf of everybody
else, on behalf

00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:44.880 align:middle line:84%
of making the human journey
a much better place,

00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:49.110 align:middle line:84%
on behalf of sensing
how we can serve

00:16:49.110 --> 00:16:52.950 align:middle line:84%
the whole with all that
we are and all that we

00:16:52.950 --> 00:16:55.570 align:middle line:90%
have to give to the whole.

00:16:55.570 --> 00:17:00.770 align:middle line:84%
The spiritual path is not about
what we can take from life,

00:17:00.770 --> 00:17:05.210 align:middle line:84%
but how we become an
instrument of transforming

00:17:05.210 --> 00:17:10.200 align:middle line:84%
the whole of life on
behalf of everyone else.

00:17:10.200 --> 00:17:13.069 align:middle line:84%
The spiritual
journey inside of you

00:17:13.069 --> 00:17:18.780 align:middle line:84%
is going to make you more
attuned to the world around you

00:17:18.780 --> 00:17:22.410 align:middle line:84%
because your intuitive,
your inner senses

