00:17:33.320 --> 00:17:38.130 align:middle line:84%
the journey of self-discovery
about yourself,

00:17:38.130 --> 00:17:42.410 align:middle line:84%
your inner nature,
who you really are,

00:17:42.410 --> 00:17:50.460 align:middle line:84%
what really drives you,
so that you can truly

00:17:50.460 --> 00:17:57.570 align:middle line:84%
respond to the needs of
others and to your own deeper

00:17:57.570 --> 00:18:01.080 align:middle line:90%
potential as a soul.

00:18:01.080 --> 00:18:06.450 align:middle line:84%
So I want to discuss invisible
facts about invisible power,

00:18:06.450 --> 00:18:09.640 align:middle line:90%
and specifically, sacred power.

00:18:09.640 --> 00:18:14.280 align:middle line:84%
You may not think about sacred
power or power as sacred,

00:18:14.280 --> 00:18:17.970 align:middle line:84%
but actually, this
is a big jewel

00:18:17.970 --> 00:18:21.990 align:middle line:90%
to put into your jewel pouch.

00:18:21.990 --> 00:18:26.910 align:middle line:84%
Sacred power is what we aspire
to on the spiritual journey,

00:18:26.910 --> 00:18:30.030 align:middle line:84%
the acquisition and
the development,

00:18:30.030 --> 00:18:36.490 align:middle line:84%
the inner development of
sacred inner authority.

00:18:36.490 --> 00:18:39.300 align:middle line:84%
And sacred power, what
do I mean by that?

00:18:39.300 --> 00:18:41.120 align:middle line:90%
Think about healing.

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:43.630 align:middle line:90%
What does it take to heal?

00:18:43.630 --> 00:18:45.810 align:middle line:84%
If you just put your
hands on someone,

00:18:45.810 --> 00:18:47.550 align:middle line:84%
nothing's going to
happen as a rule.

00:18:47.550 --> 00:18:50.670 align:middle line:90%
Maybe they'll feel a little bit.

00:18:50.670 --> 00:18:53.860 align:middle line:84%
Maybe they'll
relax a little bit.

00:18:53.860 --> 00:18:58.440 align:middle line:84%
But the chances that an
illness is really going to heal

00:18:58.440 --> 00:19:00.090 align:middle line:90%
is not likely.

00:19:00.090 --> 00:19:02.890 align:middle line:90%
It's not likely.

00:19:02.890 --> 00:19:10.210 align:middle line:84%
But could a person actually
heal from someone touching them?

00:19:10.210 --> 00:19:12.220 align:middle line:90%
And the answer there is yes.

00:19:12.220 --> 00:19:13.020 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:19:13.020 --> 00:19:15.060 align:middle line:90%
I have witnessed that.

00:19:15.060 --> 00:19:22.020 align:middle line:84%
As we blend our inner path with
prayer and faith and trust,

00:19:22.020 --> 00:19:25.560 align:middle line:84%
the quality of power
that comes through us

00:19:25.560 --> 00:19:27.540 align:middle line:90%
becomes more refined.

00:19:27.540 --> 00:19:30.990 align:middle line:84%
Because what happens
is that we become

00:19:30.990 --> 00:19:35.400 align:middle line:84%
capable of generating
and becoming

00:19:35.400 --> 00:19:44.010 align:middle line:84%
a source of creating experiences
that we no longer doubt.

00:19:44.010 --> 00:19:48.030 align:middle line:90%
Now, what is a miracle?

00:19:48.030 --> 00:19:49.710 align:middle line:84%
Obviously, a
miracle is something

00:19:49.710 --> 00:19:53.430 align:middle line:84%
that happens as a
result of sacred power.

00:19:53.430 --> 00:19:56.460 align:middle line:84%
We call something a
miracle because it's

00:19:56.460 --> 00:19:59.280 align:middle line:84%
