happens instantly.

00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:04.890 align:middle line:84%
It's something that
happens without time.

00:20:04.890 --> 00:20:10.470 align:middle line:84%
It happens out of the
flow of ordinary time.

00:20:10.470 --> 00:20:13.980 align:middle line:84%
Now, I wondered for
years, why doesn't healing

00:20:13.980 --> 00:20:16.620 align:middle line:90%
