00:20:16.620 --> 00:20:20.160 align:middle line:84%
And while I could actually talk
about this for a long time,

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:23.670 align:middle line:84%
because it's fascinating,
I'll cut to the chase.

00:20:23.670 --> 00:20:27.570 align:middle line:84%
Healing at the speed
of sacred power

00:20:27.570 --> 00:20:30.870 align:middle line:84%
would happen to
a lot more people

00:20:30.870 --> 00:20:36.800 align:middle line:84%
except that they
could not withstand

00:20:36.800 --> 00:20:40.430 align:middle line:84%
the consequence of something
happening at that speed

00:20:40.430 --> 00:20:41.630 align:middle line:90%
to them.

00:20:41.630 --> 00:20:42.860 align:middle line:90%
Isn't that amazing?

00:20:42.860 --> 00:20:44.630 align:middle line:90%
But it's true.

00:20:44.630 --> 00:20:49.200 align:middle line:84%
They could not handle the
speed of sacred power.

00:20:49.200 --> 00:20:56.250 align:middle line:84%
The force of it requires that we
develop faith in the existence

00:20:56.250 --> 00:21:00.510 align:middle line:84%
and cooperation and partnership
with the invisible world,

00:21:00.510 --> 00:21:06.750 align:middle line:84%
the capacity to partner with
the invisible world happens.

00:21:06.750 --> 00:21:11.310 align:middle line:84%
Sacred power inspires you
to empower others, not

00:21:11.310 --> 00:21:13.020 align:middle line:90%
disempower them.

