In fact, more power
pours into you.

00:21:26.170 --> 00:21:31.000 align:middle line:84%
Sacred power is an active
agent of transformation.

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:34.270 align:middle line:84%
You're not driven by greed,
but rather this understanding

00:21:34.270 --> 00:21:38.410 align:middle line:84%
that a rising tide
lifts all ships,

00:21:38.410 --> 00:21:45.430 align:middle line:84%
and that the more you help the
tide and others lift, the more

00:21:45.430 --> 00:21:50.230 align:middle line:84%
everyone, all humanity
benefits, because what is in one

00:21:50.230 --> 00:21:51.850 align:middle line:90%
is in the whole.

00:21:51.850 --> 00:21:57.160 align:middle line:84%
We are meant to treat each other
the same way heaven interacts

00:21:57.160 --> 00:21:58.540 align:middle line:90%
with us.

00:21:58.540 --> 00:22:00.610 align:middle line:84%
I just have to
share some stories,

00:22:00.610 --> 00:22:04.055 align:middle line:90%
because that is the way it is.

00:22:04.055 --> 00:22:05.180 align:middle line:90%
This is one of my favorite.

00:22:05.180 --> 00:22:08.480 align:middle line:84%
This is from "Invisible
Acts of Power."

00:22:08.480 --> 00:22:13.290 align:middle line:84%
So this man decides one night
to drive his motorcycle late

00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:14.090 align:middle line:90%
at night.

00:22:14.090 --> 00:22:16.690 align:middle line:84%
And it's wintertime, and he
thinks, what a stupid thing

00:22:16.690 --> 00:22:17.930 align:middle line:90%
to do, but I can't help it.

00:22:17.930 --> 00:22:18.835 align:middle line:90%
I want to do it.

00:22:18.835 --> 00:22:23.200 align:middle line:84%
And he's driving on this road
and he gets into black ice,

00:22:23.200 --> 00:22:27.820 align:middle line:84%
and the motorcycle slides
out because he hits a deer.

00:22:27.820 --> 00:22:31.660 align:middle line:84%
He said he saw the ice coming
right out of the woods.

00:22:31.660 --> 00:22:34.360 align:middle line:84%
He couldn't stop his
motorcycle, it was on ice,

00:22:34.360 --> 00:22:35.620 align:middle line:90%
and he hits the deer.

00:22:35.620 --> 00:22:37.630 align:middle line:84%
He goes flying off
the motorcycle,

00:22:37.630 --> 00:22:43.090 align:middle line:84%
breaks both his legs,
and the deer's dead.

00:22:43.090 --> 00:22:48.640 align:middle line:84%
And he's lying there on this
road in the country just

00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:52.330 align:middle line:84%
as the road bends, and he
thinks he's going to die,

00:22:52.330 --> 00:22:55.360 align:middle line:84%
because a car's going
to come around the bend

00:22:55.360 --> 00:22:58.030 align:middle line:84%
and he won't be able to
stop because the ice,

00:22:58.030 --> 00:23:01.240 align:middle line:84%
and he's going to
now get smashed.

00:23:01.240 --> 00:23:03.610 align:middle line:84%
He's imagining that that's
going to be his end,

00:23:03.610 --> 00:23:05.710 align:middle line:90%
so he starts praying.

00:23:05.710 --> 00:23:10.812 align:middle line:84%
And he hears footsteps
on this frozen snow,

00:23:10.812 --> 00:23:12.520 align:middle line:84%
but he can't see
anything because there's

00:23:12.520 --> 00:23:14.650 align:middle line:90%
blood in his eyes.

00:23:14.650 --> 00:23:21.070 align:middle line:84%
And a woman grabs his head
and puts his head in her lap

00:23:21.070 --> 00:23:22.060 align:middle line:90%
and says, don't worry.

00:23:22.060 --> 00:23:24.130 align:middle line:90%
There's an ambulance on its way.

00:23:24.130 --> 00:23:28.450 align:middle line:84%
He assumes she
called the ambulance.

00:23:28.450 --> 00:23:31.750 align:middle line:84%
And pretty soon, this
ambulance shows up.

00:23:31.750 --> 00:23:36.370 align:middle line:84%
And they said they happened
to be just driving.

00:23:36.370 --> 00:23:38.170 align:middle line:90%
No, nobody called.

00:23:38.170 --> 00:23:40.270 align:middle line:84%
And no, there aren't
any footsteps.

00:23:40.270 --> 00:23:44.050 align:middle line:90%
And no, there isn't any woman.

00:23:44.050 --> 00:23:49.080 align:middle line:84%
And he knew that
that was his angel.

00:23:49.080 --> 00:23:51.840 align:middle line:84%
And of course, that
changed his whole life.

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:57.810 align:middle line:84%
And that is one of so
many, many endless stories.

00:23:57.810 --> 00:24:01.960 align:middle line:84%
A man said to me, I was
going to kill myself.

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:02.850 align:middle line:90%
I was going home.

00:24:02.850 --> 00:24:04.470 align:middle line:84%
I'm standing on
the street corner.

00:24:04.470 --> 00:24:08.910 align:middle line:84%
I'm deciding, do I slit my
wrist or do I OD on pills?

00:24:08.910 --> 00:24:11.860 align:middle line:84%
I don't have enough pills, maybe
I should slit my wrists first.

00:24:11.860 --> 00:24:12.660 align:middle line:90%
And he's debating.

00:24:12.660 --> 00:24:14.260 align:middle line:90%
He's having this debate.

00:24:14.260 --> 00:24:18.435 align:middle line:84%
And he's standing there,
and a car rolls up,

00:24:18.435 --> 00:24:20.060 align:middle line:84%
and he looks at the
woman who's driving

00:24:20.060 --> 00:24:22.730 align:middle line:84%
and he just motions for
her, go, go, you go.

00:24:22.730 --> 00:24:25.180 align:middle line:84%
And she looks at him,
and instead, she's

00:24:25.180 --> 00:24:30.530 align:middle line:84%
flashes this smile at
him, and in that smile,

00:24:30.530 --> 00:24:34.800 align:middle line:84%
he decides to live because
of the way she smiled.

00:24:34.800 --> 00:24:38.770 align:middle line:84%
An invisible act as
subtle as a smile.

00:24:38.770 --> 00:24:40.960 align:middle line:84%
Or was she an angel
who just showed up

00:24:40.960 --> 00:24:46.985 align:middle line:84%
in the car in a second enough
to say, no, no, no, no, live.

00:24:46.985 --> 00:24:47.785 align:middle line:90%
Live.

00:24:47.785 --> 00:24:51.750 align:middle line:90%


00:24:51.750 --> 00:24:53.610 align:middle line:90%
That is God in the streets.

00:24:53.610 --> 00:24:56.440 align:middle line:90%
That's angels in the street.

00:24:56.440 --> 00:25:05.880 align:middle line:84%
That's how important every life
is, even in our darkest moment.

00:25:05.880 --> 00:25:09.300 align:middle line:90%
Even in our darkest moment.

00:25:09.300 --> 00:25:13.810 align:middle line:84%
These invisible acts of power
happen everywhere all the time.

00:25:13.810 --> 00:25:16.170 align:middle line:84%
And here's what you
need to understand.

00:25:16.170 --> 00:25:25.830 align:middle line:84%
We are wired to respond to each
other in the same delicate way

00:25:25.830 --> 00:25:28.660 align:middle line:90%
that heaven responds to us.

00:25:28.660 --> 00:25:32.160 align:middle line:84%
It is one huge,
breathing apparatus.

00:25:32.160 --> 00:25:34.700 align:middle line:90%


00:25:34.700 --> 00:25:37.910 align:middle line:84%
We breathe together
with heaven all the time

00:25:37.910 --> 00:25:39.620 align:middle line:90%
and every prayer is heard.

00:25:39.620 --> 00:25:42.780 align:middle line:90%


00:25:42.780 --> 00:25:46.440 align:middle line:84%
Every single prayer and
every action is known.

00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:52.550 align:middle line:84%
And while I cannot prove that,
there is not one part of me

00:25:52.550 --> 00:25:54.420 align:middle line:90%
that doubts it.

00:25:54.420 --> 00:25:57.770 align:middle line:84%
And if your world feels better
with doubt, you go right ahead.

00:25:57.770 --> 00:25:59.730 align:middle line:84%
But I have to tell
you something,

00:25:59.730 --> 00:26:03.070 align:middle line:90%
try believing it for a week.

00:26:03.070 --> 00:26:07.400 align:middle line:84%
And when something
wonderful happens,

00:26:07.400 --> 00:26:11.590 align:middle line:84%
don't tell yourself
it's a coincidence.

00:26:11.590 --> 00:26:13.750 align:middle line:90%
Use the right language.

00:26:13.750 --> 00:26:17.830 align:middle line:90%
Tell yourself, it's grace.

